130
00:10:44,090 --> 00:10:46,090
- ¿Está fresco, Rainer?
- Eso espero.

131
00:10:46,752 --> 00:10:48,752
- Buenos días, Rainer.
- Sinan.

132
00:10:50,866 --> 00:10:52,558
